reviews.title: Great except for a few problems
reviews.comment: I love this app. I have two problems with it though. If you guess wrong or spell a word wrong you get an error message and it closes on you. The hints could be better. Maybe if it gave you the first letter of the word when you ask for a letter. That would be a big help. Or maybe if there was a riddle for a clue. That would be cool too.
